  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate Subjects With Turner Syndrome Treated With Growth Hormone</brief_title>
  <official_title>Characterization of Subjects With Turner Syndrome Treated With Growth Hormone in the National Cooperative Growth Study (NCGS)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
